    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean used car in mint condition. It starts, runs, and drives exactly as it should, with a very well-kept interior, clean exterior, and only minimal signs of prior use. This is the kind of vehicle a buyer can feel confident about if they want something that presents extremely well and needs nothing beyond routine ownership.",
