    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle for someone who wants dependable basic transportation without overspending. This car shows its age, but it offers a great entry point for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing an affordable runabout. Priced to reflect its condition and deliver strong value, it\u2019s a straightforward opportunity at an accessible price.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts up, gets you where you need to go, and could be a great fit for someone who wants dependable basic transport without spending a fortune. It\u2019s also a nice option for a first car, a backup commuter, or a handy project for someone who enjoys tinkering. Priced fairly for what it is, and offered by someone who believes in being straightforward and easy to deal with.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong candidate for a budget-friendly project or dependable beater with good bones. This car shows its age cosmetically and is being sold in poor condition, but it still offers honest utility, a straightforward mechanical layout, and the kind of usability that makes it worth a look for someone who values function over finish. Ideal for a commuter backup, first DIY project, or parts-friendly platform. Priced to move and leave room in the budget for the next owner to sort the details.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way to get on the road. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest character you notice right away\u2014the sort of driver that still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who appreciates a vehicle with personality, whether you need a budget-friendly commuter, a practical backup, or a project to make your own. There\u2019s a rugged, lived-in charm here that gives it presence, and for the right buyer, it offers real potential without a big upfront cost. If you\u2019re looking for something inexpensive, straightforward, and full of possibility, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Dependable, affordable, and priced for smart value, this vehicle is a practical choice for anyone seeking straightforward transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a solid opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer, commuter, or backup vehicle. A candid, high-value offering from a trusted seller.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants a cheap daily, a handy backup, or a fun little project to tinker with. It\u2019s being sold honestly as-is, and the price reflects that, but if you\u2019re after something budget-friendly and approachable, this could be a great fit. Come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right one for you.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project with a strong-running powertrain, responsive throttle, and a chassis that still feels planted. Starts, moves, and has the kind of honest mechanical feel enthusiasts look for in a budget build, commuter, or parts donor. Not a show car and it will need cosmetic and reconditioning work, but the core package is appealing: usable drivetrain, complete setup, and plenty of upside for someone who knows their way around maintenance. A great chance to get into a capable platform at an affordable entry point.",
      "price": 6850.0,
